history.text: Hi. How are you today?
Hey I'm great, how are you doing today?
Just fine. Hey, I watched a movie a while back and it popper into my head. Frozen.
Frozen is a good movie, did you enjoy it?
I did. I remember seeing it in the Theatres back in 2013.
I saw it earlier this month for the first time, whos your favorite characteR?
I actually really enjoyed Kristoff. How about you?
Elsa because my daughter loved her!
lol. My kids loved that movie. I wanted to watch is because of the actresses who voices Anna and Elsa.
Exactly thats why I went as well, do you know if they're making a sequel?
I heard they might make one, but I don't know for sure. The Frozen short film they made didn't go over well with audiences.
I didnt see that, how was it?
I didn't see it either, just heard it was "20 minutes I'll never get back."
Oh that sounds awful hopefully my daughter doesn't want to go, we should all go to the sequel sometime.
I agree. When it comes out. That should be fun. Do you think they'll keep the same cast?
I think they'll change some of it up just to keep it fresh but keep the main characters, what about you?
I agree. Keep the main cast and they'll be fine.
What was your favorite part about the movie?
The reindeer. lol
Absolutely agreed.
Did you know the guy who played Kristoff was actually a famous broadway singer?
I had no idea but that makes sense, hes got the voice for sure, know any other cool factS?
A few. The movie was based off of a Hans Christian Andersen story called "the snow queen".
Im gonna tell my daughter about all these, I'll have to check out the book.
I think it's a short story. Maybe you should read it first. A lot of his stories don't have happy endings.
I will have to to make sure theres nothing too bad, it was a great movie thats for sure
I agree. Wonderful movie.
What was your favorite song in the movie?
Definitely "let it go", you?
I guess I'm the odd ball. the song kristoff sang to the reindeer.

uid2response.feedback: The responder made me feel more intrigued about frozen, i didn't know some things about it that he told me.
